#: ../../SO3.md:166
msgid "The proportion of land in each drought intensity class is calculated for each reporting year as a percentage of the total land area."
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO3.md:168
msgid "For each of the SPI-12 grids in the baseline and reporting period, the number of cells falling under each of the SPI drought intensity classes is counted (cellCount). Then, for each reporting year, the percentage of the total land area in each drought intensity class is calculated. The formula is as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO3.md:170
msgid "$P_{ij} = \\frac{cellCount_{ij}}{Total\\ number\\ of\\ cells} \\times 100$"
