msgid "Good Practice Guidance for National Reporting on UNCCD Strategic Objective 3. Chapter 1. Level 1 Indicator (<https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-national-reporting-unccd-strategic-objective-3-mitigate-adapt>)"
